title: The Cheese Stick and the Mountain
features: Join plucky cheese stick Skyline as she goes on an adventurous hike up a mountain. What will happen when she finds a secret door in the side of the mountain? She will have to use all of her potions to make it through to the other side . . . but what awaits her when she gets there?! The Cheese Stick and the Mountain is the first book by 6 year-old author Emily J. Alexander. She was inspired by her favorite books from the fantasy and adventure genres.
description: Emily J. Alexander is a 6 year-old first grader from the state of Washington. She enjoys reading fantasy and adventure books.
